### Get transactions with pagination, filters and sorting

GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?{{exchange}}&{{sorting}}&{{pagination}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### GET STATISTICS ABOUT TRANSACTIONS
@excludeCategories = excludeCategories=myAccount,investments
@yearAndMonth = year=2023

GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/statistics?{{PLN}}&{{type}}&{{yearAndMonth}}&{{excludeCategories}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### GET TOTALS FOR TRANSACTIONS
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/totals?{{excludeCategories}}&startDate=2024-12-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

