### Create new standard transaction

# @name createTransaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions/standard
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "date": "2026-01-24",
  "description": "VERY NEW TRANSACTION",
  "amount": 1.70,
  "currency": "PLN",
  "category": "transport",
  "transactionType": "expense",
  "paymentMethod": "card",
  "account": "mBank"
}

### CREATE NEW EXCHANGE TRANSACTIONS
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions/exchange
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "date": "2026-01-24",
  "additionalDescription": "some additional desc",  
  "amountExpense": 20,
  "amountIncome": 84.23,
  "currencyExpense": "EUR",
  "currencyIncome": "PLN",
  "account": "revolut",
  "paymentMethod": "bankTransfer"
}

